div.p:


This in all Creatures is only moveable,
except as ſome affirm in the Crocodile,
who moves the upper only.

We will begin with the Superior;
but firſt I muſt inform you, that ſince
both Extremities are double, I ſhall
only ſpeak of them in the ſingular number,
for by demonſtrating one ſide,
you at the ſame time ſhew the other.
